          </Base:Description>
          <Base:Description type="look">
             A black steel and ivory myr horn snaphaunce pistol with a short, polished steel barrel and a solid grip crafted from an ivory myr horn, ending in a thinly rounded butt. It is a weapon involving a cock which holds a sharpened piece of flint and gunpowder which can fire a bullet with great force. It is decorated with an exotic white steel filigree. {? | $(this.firearm:loaded) | This pistol is loaded. }
